# Client TypeScript

## Imports

- Path alias: `@/` → `client/src/` (never deep `../../../`).
- `import type { … }` for type-only imports (`verbatimModuleSyntax`).
- Zod: `import z from "zod"` (default import).

## Hooks & utilities

- Custom hooks: `export const useFoo = () => { … }` in `hooks/use-foo.ts` (kebab-case filename).
- Prefer arrow `const` exports; plain `export function` only for non-React helpers when it reads clearer (`getFieldErrors`, `isLanguage`).

## Types

- Shared props/types exposed from modules: prefix with **`T`** when reused across files (`TDialogType`, `TDefaultDialogFormPublicProps`).
- PocketBase records: extend `RecordModel` in `@/types/pocketbase.ts`; use `Collections` / `CollectionName` for collection ids.
- Discriminated unions over `any`; `any` only where already established (TanStack Form instance in `Default.form.tsx`).

## PocketBase

```ts
import { pb } from "@/lib/pocketbase";
import { collection } from "@/lib/pocketbase"; // typed CRUD when possible

await pb.collection("users").authWithPassword(email, password);
await collection("bosses").getFullList();
```

- Dev API base: `VITE_PB_URL=/` (same-origin via Vite proxy) — never `""` (breaks URLs on nested routes).
- Auth state: `pb.authStore`; app context via `UserProvider` / `useUserContext`.

## Router

- Route tree in `router.tsx`; route modules in `src/routes/`.
- Auth gates in `beforeLoad` with `redirect({ to: "/login" })` and `context.isAuthenticated`.
- Page components live in `pages/`, not inline in route files.

## State & dialogs

- Zustand stores: `*.store.ts`, `create<Store>(…)`, export hook + imperative helpers (`openDialog`, `closeAlertDialog`).
- Global UI: `GlobalDialog`, `AppAlertDialog` — register dialogs in store/registry, don’t mount one-offs in random pages.

## i18n

- `useTranslation("namespace")` with JSON under `src/i18n/locales/{en,fr}/`.
- User language field on `users` record; use `Language` from `@/types/language`.
